Gnome Terminal configuration:
- use Hack fonts
- move tabs to bottom
- do not show menubar
- keybindings
|----------------+-------------|
| New Tab        | Ctrl-T      |
| Next Tab       | Shift-Right |
| Previuos Tab   | Shift-Left  |
| Toggle Menubar | Ctrl-M      |
|----------------+-------------|
- default profile with
	- 'fish' shell
